    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>Financial arrangements must be detailed in the Memorandum of Agreement between the University and the partner organisation. If you have a specific question about the financial agreement, contact the partnerships team in Governance and Quality Enhancement (GQE). All signed contracts are held in the GQE office.</p>]]></Value>
